This repository reproduces the core ideas of *Self‑Composing Policies for Scalable Continual Reinforcement Learning*.
The `reproduce.sh` script installs dependencies, runs the two benchmark experiments, and writes a combined `results.csv`.

The implementation is intentionally lightweight: it focuses on the core architecture and shows that CompoNet can be integrated seamlessly with SAC and PPO.

Feel free to modify hyper‑parameters or extend the experiment to other environments.